I"n<blockquote>
  <p>“The world is not a solid continent of facts sprinkled by a few lakes of uncertainties, but a vast ocean of uncertainties speckled by a few islands of calibrated and stabilized forms.”</p>
</blockquote>

<p>~ Bruno Latour, We Have Never Been Modern</p>

